"{\"uid\": \"timesrepublican.com-opinion-columnists-2024-08-no-bragging-on-this-olympics-iowa-angle\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Aug 6, 2024 Photo by Jared Strong/Iowa Capital Dispatch The North Raccoon River routinely has elevated levels of nitrate contamination.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 136, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Aug 6, 2024 Photo\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 17}, {\"ngram\": \"Jared Strong\", \"from\": 21, \"to\": 33}, {\"ngram\": \"The North Raccoon River\", \"from\": 56, \"to\": 79}, {\"ngram\": \"elevated levels\", \"from\": 94, \"to\": 109}, {\"ngram\": \"nitrate contamination\", \"from\": 113, \"to\": 134}]}, {\"sentence\": \"During the 40 years I was a newspaper editor/manager, I strived to ensure the staff incorporated context into their articles.\", \"from\": 138, \"to\": 263, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 40 years\", \"from\": 145, \"to\": 157}, {\"ngram\": \"a newspaper editor\", \"from\": 164, \"to\": 182}, {\"ngram\": \"/manager\", \"from\": 182, \"to\": 190}, {\"ngram\": \"the staff\", \"from\": 212, \"to\": 221}, {\"ngram\": \"context\", \"from\": 235, \"to\": 242}, {\"ngram\": \"their articles\", \"from\": 248, \"to\": 262}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sometimes, in a journalistic shorthand, that was described \\\"the Iowa angle.\\\"\", \"from\": 264, \"to\": 340, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 328, \"end\": 332, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iowa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.7367592762326985e-24, \"text\": \"Iowa\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iowa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iowa\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a journalistic shorthand\", \"from\": 278, \"to\": 302}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If there was a mass murder in Iowa, I would dip into my stash of clippings and find the list of the worst mass killings in Iowa history.\", \"from\": 342, \"to\": 478, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 372, \"end\": 376, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iowa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.7367592762326985e-24, \"text\": \"Iowa\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iowa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iowa\"}, {\"begin\": 465, \"end\": 469, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iowa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.7367592762326985e-24, \"text\": \"Iowa\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iowa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iowa\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a mass murder\", \"from\": 355, \"to\": 368}, {\"ngram\": \"my stash\", \"from\": 395, \"to\": 403}, {\"ngram\": \"clippings\", \"from\": 407, \"to\": 416}, {\"ngram\": \"the list\", \"from\": 426, \"to\": 434}, {\"ngram\": \"the worst mass killings\", \"from\": 438, \"to\": 461}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That allowed us to give context to the magnitude of the tragedy.\", \"from\": 479, \"to\": 543, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 492, \"to\": 494}, {\"ngram\": \"context\", \"from\": 503, \"to\": 510}, {\"ngram\": \"the magnitude\", \"from\": 514, \"to\": 527}, {\"ngram\": \"the tragedy\", \"from\": 531, \"to\": 542}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The same with tornadoes and floods.\", \"from\": 545, \"to\": 580, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"tornadoes\", \"from\": 559, \"to\": 568}, {\"ngram\": \"floods\", \"from\": 573, \"to\": 579}]}, {\"sentence\": \"How does the number of deaths compare with the worst of these nightmares we have experienced in the past?\", \"from\": 581, \"to\": 686, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the number\", \"from\": 590, \"to\": 600}, {\"ngram\": \"deaths\", \"from\": 604, \"to\": 610}, {\"ngram\": \"these nightmares\", \"from\": 637, \"to\": 653}, {\"ngram\": \"the past\", \"from\": 677, \"to\": 685}]}, {\"sentence\": \"During the Vietnam War, and later during the Gulf wars, we turned to bound desk calendars where we pasted clippings to track the running tally of deaths of Iowa soldiers.\", \"from\": 688, \"to\": 858, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 844, \"end\": 848, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iowa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.7367592762326985e-24, \"text\": \"Iowa\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iowa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iowa\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Vietnam War\", \"from\": 695, \"to\": 710}, {\"ngram\": \"the Gulf wars\", \"from\": 729, \"to\": 742}, {\"ngram\": \"bound desk calendars\", \"from\": 757, \"to\": 777}, {\"ngram\": \"clippings\", \"from\": 794, \"to\": 803}, {\"ngram\": \"the running tally\", \"from\": 813, \"to\": 830}, {\"ngram\": \"deaths\", \"from\": 834, \"to\": 840}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So, over this past weekend a friend and I pawed through statistics to provide important Iowa context when Belgium's mixed relay triathlon team pulled out of the Olympic competition in Paris.\", \"from\": 860, \"to\": 1050, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 948, \"end\": 952, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iowa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.7367592762326985e-24, \"text\": \"Iowa\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iowa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iowa\"}, {\"begin\": 966, \"end\": 973, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\", \"score\": 0.9999999945434865, \"rank\": 5.43911329190894e-09, \"text\": \"Belgium\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\"}, {\"begin\": 1044, \"end\": 1049, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.44388458386514e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this past weekend\", \"from\": 869, \"to\": 886}, {\"ngram\": \"statistics\", \"from\": 916, \"to\": 926}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic competition\", \"from\": 1017, \"to\": 1040}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Belgium's decision was made after one of its athletes became ill and was hospitalized, reportedly for an E. coli infection, after she swam in the River Seine earlier in the competition.\", \"from\": 1052, \"to\": 1237, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1052, \"end\": 1059, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\", \"score\": 0.9999999945434865, \"rank\": 5.43911329190894e-09, \"text\": \"Belgium\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\"}, {\"begin\": 1198, \"end\": 1209, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"River Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"its athletes\", \"from\": 1093, \"to\": 1105}, {\"ngram\": \"an E. coli infection\", \"from\": 1154, \"to\": 1174}, {\"ngram\": \"the competition\", \"from\": 1221, \"to\": 1236}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The same day as the announcement about Claire Michel, Olympic organizers canceled a training session for the swimming leg of the triathlon because the Seine's water pollution levels were too high.\", \"from\": 1238, \"to\": 1434, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1277, \"end\": 1290, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Claire_Michel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Claire Michel\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Claire_Michel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Claire_Michel\"}, {\"begin\": 1389, \"end\": 1394, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.999990507093609, \"rank\": 9.492996593058805e-06, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the announcement\", \"from\": 1254, \"to\": 1270}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic organizers\", \"from\": 1292, \"to\": 1310}, {\"ngram\": \"a training session\", \"from\": 1320, \"to\": 1338}, {\"ngram\": \"the swimming leg\", \"from\": 1343, \"to\": 1359}, {\"ngram\": \"the triathlon\", \"from\": 1363, \"to\": 1376}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The quality of the Seine's water has been a persistent worry leading up to this year's Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 1436, \"to\": 1537, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1455, \"end\": 1460, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.999990507093609, \"rank\": 9.492996593058805e-06, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The quality\", \"from\": 1436, \"to\": 1447}, {\"ngram\": \"a persistent worry\", \"from\": 1478, \"to\": 1496}, {\"ngram\": \"this year's Olympic Games\", \"from\": 1511, \"to\": 1536}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The pollution levels forced organizers to consider delaying, or even canceling, some outdoor swimming events.\", \"from\": 1538, \"to\": 1647, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The pollution levels\", \"from\": 1538, \"to\": 1558}, {\"ngram\": \"organizers\", \"from\": 1566, \"to\": 1576}, {\"ngram\": \"delaying\", \"from\": 1589, \"to\": 1597}, {\"ngram\": \"some outdoor swimming events\", \"from\": 1618, \"to\": 1646}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is where the Iowa angle comes into the picture - and it provides some interesting context for the news out of Paris.\", \"from\": 1649, \"to\": 1770, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1667, \"end\": 1671, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iowa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.7367592762326985e-24, \"text\": \"Iowa\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iowa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iowa\"}, {\"begin\": 1764, \"en